creditline: Gift of Mrs. Fred C. Watson in memory of her mother Mrs. Weed Munro of Minneapolis
description: This shawl was not found in an inventory in the early 1970's. It was again not found in an 1997 inventory. There are no measurements or photographs of the object. The textile dep't. has no records or cards for the object. A search for this object in April of 2000 did not locate the object. 4/28/2000  KK
title: Shawl
